Package: OncoTree
Title: Expose the OncoTree API for R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Marcel", "Ramos", , "marcel.ramos@sph.cuny.edu", c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3242-0582"))
Description: Expose the OncoTree API for R. OncoTree is a standardized ontology
  of cancer terms that is used to annotate cancer data. This package provides a
  set of functions to query the OncoTree API and retrieve information about
  cancer types, subtypes, and their relationships.
License: Artistic-2.0
Depends: AnVIL
Imports:
  dplyr,
  methods
